text: Vrapče is a village in Vogošća municipality, near Sarajevo, Federation of Bosnia and Herzegovina, Bosnia and Herzegovina. ==Population== ===Ethnic composition, 1991 census=== total: 59 * Serbs - 36 (61.01%) * Muslims by nationality - 23 (38.98%) ==History== ==References== * Official results from the book: Ethnic composition of Bosnia-Herzegovina population, by municipalities and settlements, 1991. census, Zavod za statistiku Bosne i Hercegovine - Bilten no.234, Sarajevo 1991.
